## Technical Specifications

### Core Features
- Universal Token Support: ERC20 tokens and native ETH through unified interface
- Activity-Based Management: Flexible organization using bytes32 activity keys
- Optimized Storage: Single storage slot per lock (128-bit amount + 64-bit duration + 64-bit start time)
- Security Patterns: ReentrancyGuard + Checks-Interactions-Effects + secure transfer patterns
- Flexible Duration: 1 second to 1 year lock periods with precise timestamp control
  
### Gas Optimization
- Single storage slot packing reduces SSTORE costs by ~15,000 gas per lock
- Efficient mapping structure minimizes storage reads
- Optimized event emission for comprehensive logging with minimal overhead
- Simplified native ETH transfers without gas restrictions for improved compatibility
  
### Security Measures
- OpenZeppelin ReentrancyGuard protection against reentrancy attacks
- Secure native ETH transfers with proper error handling and success validation
- Comprehensive input validation and custom error handling for gas efficiency
- Secure deletion of storage after successful unlocks to prevent state inconsistencies
- Checks-Interactions-Effects pattern implementation for maximum security

